                Trusted Tax, Bookkeeping, and Real Estate Tax Support for Individuals, Investors, and Businesses

                Peter’s Tax & Bookkeeping Solution is a full-service tax preparation and bookkeeping firm serving
                individuals, business owners, and real estate investors throughout the Bay Area, with a strong and
                established presence in Solano County.

                Since 2015, we have assisted more than 400 clients, including salaried professionals, small business
                owners, landlords, real estate investors, and active stock market participants. We have proudly served
                the Solano County community since 2016.

                We understand that today’s financial lives are complex. Income may come from employment,
                self-employment, rental properties, stock investments, or multiple business entities. Combined with
                constantly changing tax laws, this complexity requires experience, accuracy, and careful planning.

                Our approach is thorough and detail-driven. We focus on compliance, documentation, and long-term
                planning to help reduce risk, avoid costly mistakes, and support sound financial decisions.

                Our mission is simple: provide reliable guidance, ensure accuracy, and help you keep more of what you
                earn—legally and responsibly.y,
